quotes.title: St. Jerome
quotes.desc: Good, better, best. Never let it rest. 'Til your good is better and your better is best.

quotes.title: E. Joseph Cossman
quotes.desc: The best way to remember your wife's birthday is to forget it once.

quotes.title: Mark Twain
quotes.desc: The secret of getting ahead is getting started.

quotes.title: George Sand
quotes.desc: There is only one happiness in this life, to love and be loved.

quotes.title: Albert Einstein
quotes.desc: It is the supreme art of the teacher to awaken joy in creative expression and knowledge.

quotes.title: Hugh Grant
quotes.desc: I frequently dream of having tea with the Queen.

quotes.title: Winston Churchill
quotes.desc: Attitude is a little thing that makes a big difference.
